---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Use Cases — SolanaForensics" description="How law enforcement, compliance teams, and fraud investigators use SolanaForensics for Solana wallet tracing and forensic evidence reporting.">

  <div style="height: 70px;"></div>

  <section class="page-hero grid-bg">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="tag">// Use Cases</div>
        <h1>Deployed across <span class="accent">investigation verticals.</span></h1>
        <p class="page-hero-sub">SolanaForensics serves professionals who need evidentiary-grade blockchain intelligence.</p>
        <a href="https://t.me/solanaforensics_bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary hero-cta">Start Investigating →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="node-graph" viewBox="0 0 320 280" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="200" y2="40" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.25"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="260" y2="120" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.25"/>
          <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="60" y2="160" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.25"/>
          <line x1="60" y1="160" x2="160" y2="200" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.2"/>
          <line x1="160" y1="200" x2="260" y2="120" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.2"/>
          <line x1="200" y1="40" x2="160" y2="200" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="0.75" opacity="0.15" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
          <line x1="260" y1="120" x2="240" y2="240" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.2"/>
          <line x1="160" y1="200" x2="240" y2="240" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="0.75" opacity="0.15"/>
          <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="160" y2="200" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="0.75" opacity="0.1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
          <circle cx="80" cy="60" r="8" fill="var(--bg-card)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" class="node node-1"/>
          <circle cx="80" cy="60" r="3" fill="var(--accent)" class="node-dot node-1"/>
          <circle cx="200" cy="40" r="10" fill="var(--bg-card)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" class="node node-2"/>
          <circle cx="200" cy="40" r="4" fill="var(--danger)" class="node-dot node-2"/>
          <circle cx="260" cy="120" r="7" fill="var(--bg-card)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" class="node node-3"/>
          <circle cx="260" cy="120" r="3" fill="var(--accent)" class="node-dot node-3"/>
          <circle cx="60" cy="160" r="6" fill="var(--bg-card)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" class="node node-4"/>
          <circle cx="60" cy="160" r="2.5" fill="var(--accent)" class="node-dot node-4"/>
          <circle cx="160" cy="200" r="9" fill="var(--bg-card)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5" class="node node-5"/>
          <circle cx="160" cy="200" r="3.5" fill="var(--accent)" class="node-dot node-5"/>
          <circle cx="240" cy="240" r="6" fill="var(--bg-card)" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1" class="node node-6"/>
          <circle cx="240" cy="240" r="2.5" fill="var(--success)" class="node-dot node-6"/>
          <text x="200" y="18" fill="var(--danger)" font-family="var(--mono)" font-size="8" text-anchor="middle" opacity="0.6">FLAGGED</text>
          <text x="240" y="265" fill="var(--success)" font-family="var(--mono)" font-size="7" text-anchor="middle" opacity="0.5">CEX KYC</text>
          <text x="45" y="55" fill="var(--accent)" font-family="var(--mono)" font-size="7" opacity="0.4">SRC</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="uc-sections">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="uc-block" id="law-enforcement">
        <div class="uc-label">
          <span class="mono uc-num">// 01</span>
          <h2>Law Enforcement</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-content">
          <p>Police forces and financial crime units need blockchain evidence that meets courtroom standards. SolanaForensics provides a full forensic chain of custody, structured reports aligned with law enforcement submission formats, and real-time monitoring tools for active investigations.</p>
          <div class="uc-scenarios">
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                Crypto Fraud Investigations
              </h4>
              <p>Trace funds from victim wallets to exchange accounts, identify withdrawal points for KYC requests, and build a complete evidence package for arrest warrants.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                Investment Scam Takedowns
              </h4>
              <p>Map the full financial structure of fraudulent investment platforms — identify operators, trace fund extraction patterns, and quantify total victim losses.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                Money Laundering Cases
              </h4>
              <p>Document layering techniques used to obscure criminal proceeds and present them in formats suitable for prosecution.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="uc-block" id="compliance">
        <div class="uc-label">
          <span class="mono uc-num">// 02</span>
          <h2>Compliance & AML</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-content">
          <p>Financial intelligence units and compliance teams need automated tools to detect suspicious on-chain activity and generate Suspicious Activity Reports (SARs) and FIAU submissions efficiently.</p>
          <div class="uc-scenarios">
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="m9 15 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
                SAR Generation
              </h4>
              <p>Automatically generate Suspicious Activity Reports with full transaction evidence and risk scoring for regulatory bodies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="m9 15 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
                Counterparty Risk Assessment
              </h4>
              <p>Assess the risk profile of counterparties before transacting, based on wallet history and network associations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="m9 15 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
                Travel Rule Compliance
              </h4>
              <p>Identify and document originator and beneficiary information for VASP-to-VASP transactions above threshold amounts.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="uc-block" id="fraud">
        <div class="uc-label">
          <span class="mono uc-num">// 03</span>
          <h2>Fraud Investigation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-content">
          <p>Private fraud investigators, corporate security teams, and forensic accountants use SolanaForensics to reconstruct complex fraud schemes and identify the individuals who benefited.</p>
          <div class="uc-scenarios">
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
                Exit Scam Analysis
              </h4>
              <p>Reconstruct the timeline and mechanics of rug pulls and exit scams, identify founders' wallets, and quantify proceeds extracted from investors.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
                DeFi Exploit Tracing
              </h4>
              <p>Trace exploit proceeds from flash loan attacks and protocol exploits through DEXes and bridges to final destinations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
                Insider Trading Detection
              </h4>
              <p>Identify wallets with foreknowledge of token launches or protocol exploits based on pre-event positioning patterns.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="uc-block" id="legal">
        <div class="uc-label">
          <span class="mono uc-num">// 04</span>
          <h2>Legal & Asset Recovery</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-content">
          <p>Legal counsel and asset recovery specialists use our platform to build blockchain evidence packages for civil litigation, freezing orders, and victim restitution proceedings.</p>
          <div class="uc-scenarios">
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1z"/><path d="m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1z"/><path d="M7 21h10"/><path d="M12 3v18"/><path d="M3 7h2c2 0 5-1 7-2 2 1 5 2 7 2h2"/></svg>
                Asset Freezing Orders
              </h4>
              <p>Identify and document wallet addresses holding misappropriated assets to support injunction applications and preservation orders.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1z"/><path d="m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1z"/><path d="M7 21h10"/><path d="M12 3v18"/><path d="M3 7h2c2 0 5-1 7-2 2 1 5 2 7 2h2"/></svg>
                Victim Restitution
              </h4>
              <p>Identify recoverable assets still on-chain and prioritise wallets for enforcement action in victim recovery proceedings.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario card">
              <h4>
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1z"/><path d="m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1z"/><path d="M7 21h10"/><path d="M12 3v18"/><path d="M3 7h2c2 0 5-1 7-2 2 1 5 2 7 2h2"/></svg>
                Litigation Support
              </h4>
              <p>Provide expert-witness-ready forensic reports and transaction evidence packages for arbitration and court proceedings.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bottom-cta">
    <div class="container bottom-cta-inner">
      <div class="cta-glow"></div>
      <div class="tag">// Start Investigating</div>
      <h2>Start investigating on Telegram.</h2>
      <p>Open @solanaforensics_bot and run your first investigation in under 60 seconds.</p>
      <a href="https://t.me/solanaforensics_bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary cta-btn-lg">Start Investigating →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const blocks = document.querySelectorAll('.uc-block');
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.add('uc-visible');
        const cards = entry.target.querySelectorAll('.scenario');
        cards.forEach((card, i) => {
          (card as HTMLElement).style.transitionDelay = `${i * 150}ms`;
          card.classList.add('card-visible');
        });
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.15 });

  blocks.forEach(block => observer.observe(block));
</script>

<style>
/* HERO */
.page-hero {
  padding: 5rem 0 2.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.page-hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -80px;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 80px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 8, 16, 0), var(--bg));
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 1;
}

.hero-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
  gap: 3rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.page-hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  max-width: 700px;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.page-hero-sub {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  max-width: 540px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.hero-cta {
  margin-top: 2rem;
}

.hero-visual {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.node-graph {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 320px;
  opacity: 0.55;
}

.node {
  animation: nodePulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.node-1 { animation-delay: 0s; }
.node-2 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
.node-3 { animation-delay: 1s; }
.node-4 { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
.node-5 { animation-delay: 2s; }
.node-6 { animation-delay: 2.5s; }

@keyframes nodePulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

/* SECTIONS */
.uc-sections {
  padding: 3rem 0 7rem;
}

.uc-block {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
  gap: 5rem;
  padding: 5rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  position: relative;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(30px);
  transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
}

.uc-block.uc-visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

.uc-block::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 80px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--accent);
  opacity: 0.3;
}

.uc-block:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}
.uc-block:last-child::after {
  display: none;
}

/* VISUAL HIERARCHY */
.uc-label {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
}

.uc-num {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.uc-label h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; }

.uc-content > p {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  max-width: 600px;
}

/* CARDS */
.uc-scenarios {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.25rem;
  background: transparent;
}

.scenario {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  padding: 1.75rem;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(20px);
}

.scenario.card-visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
  transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
}

.scenario::before {
  border-radius: 10px 0 0 10px;
}

.scenario:hover {
  border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  background: rgba(15, 20, 35, 0.8);
  box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.scenario h4 {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--text);
}

.scenario h4 svg {
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.scenario p {
  font-size: 0.83rem;
  color: rgb(160, 170, 190);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

/* BOTTOM CTA */
.bottom-cta {
  background: var(--bg-2);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 6rem 0;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.bottom-cta-inner {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.cta-glow {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 500px;
  height: 300px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.bottom-cta h2 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.bottom-cta p {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  max-width: 480px;
  margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
}

.cta-btn-lg {
  padding: 1.1rem 2.75rem;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  animation: ctaPulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes ctaPulse {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); }
  50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4); }
}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero-visual { display: none; }
  .uc-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  .uc-scenarios { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .page-hero { padding: 4rem 0 2rem; }
  .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 3rem); }
  .page-hero-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .uc-sections { padding: 2rem 0 3.5rem; }
  .uc-block { padding: 3rem 0; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .uc-label h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .uc-scenarios { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
  .scenario { padding: 1.25rem; }
  .scenario h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .scenario p { font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .bottom-cta { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .bottom-cta h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.25rem); }
  .cta-btn-lg { padding: 0.875rem 2rem; font-size: 0.82rem; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .page-hero { padding: 3rem 0 1.5rem; }
  .uc-sections { padding: 1rem 0 2.5rem; }
  .uc-block { padding: 2.5rem 0; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .uc-content > p { font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .uc-scenarios { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.875rem; }
  .scenario { padding: 1.125rem; }
  .scenario h4 svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
  .bottom-cta { padding: 3rem 0; }
  .bottom-cta p { font-size: 0.88rem; }
  .cta-glow { width: 300px; height: 200px; }
}

@media (max-width: 320px) {
  .uc-label h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .uc-num { font-size: 0.85rem; }
}
</style>
